{"tid":99493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國客遭猛虎撕咬 目擊者：佢跨圍欄入園逗虎","createTime":"2017-01-29T08:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T08:47:46.000Z","uid":22736,"like":169,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b19af32af5fc0f9bc4623ace285523ff48c66780","tid":99493,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:55:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170129&amp;guid=56238048&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170129%26guid%3D56238048%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=9P9Iq%2B49TWHZ5%2Bjigqrf1mN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=8c5b92b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170129%26guid%3D56238048%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=b0ef5ea8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170129&amp;guid=56238048&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n浙江寧波雅戈爾動物園今日下午2時30分左右，發生老虎咬人事件！有目擊者稱，被咬者為一名遊客，近距離逗老虎時，被其咬入園內。目前工作人員正用炮仗驅趕老虎。從現場圖片可見，被叼入園內的遊客滿臉血，躺在地上，老虎則一直在其身側徘徊不去。據雅戈爾動物園工作人員說，受傷遊客為男性，年齡不詳。目前已送至醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n而據一名目擊者稱，事發時虎山內有飼養員在餵老虎，一名男遊客越過隔離欄，跳進虎山近距離逗虎時，被一隻老虎拖咬，其他進食中的老虎見狀，也圍向該名遊客。事發後，動物園工作人員曾用炮仗、水槍、鳴槍等方式驅趕老虎，公安、醫療人員也趕到現場。<br />\n<br />\n截至下午3時許，動物園仍在救援，虎山附近遊覽區依舊有上百名遊客逗留。據遊客稱，虎山與遊客遊覽區之間有一條河相隔，要進入虎山，必須越過河才行。<br />\n<br />\n寧波雅戈爾動物園前身是寧波東錢湖野生動物園，位於東錢湖旅遊度假區內，佔地1,900多畝，院內動物有200多個品種近萬頭動物，是中國水域面積最大的野生動物園。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cw2boMr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCw2boMr.jpg&h=be0fb60c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/165536_bbaed7985e462e5379d27e991cacc8d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F165536_bbaed7985e462e5379d27e991cacc8d9.jpg&h=8c565b42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b96c4bfecfccb654c8710799907c2602006c5f22","tid":99493,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"1dc7bddc3437bb3fbd9fe4a524c1bb73b70d369c","tid":99493,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:07:01.000Z","msg":"on9 冇藥醫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7abc01dc84ffae148fc9c24314dec04c5fa7295","tid":99493,"uid":23974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:09:25.000Z","msg":"紫色底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0f4d415db327d1000e7dd096e12a55be8604e3","tid":99493,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2a1fac9094560a3fa3f7dbeff98b8f2d3876a8","tid":99493,"uid":6313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..."},{"pid":"8977381fef49b6ca7d9767a7a3c4107a79ec63d1","tid":99493,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:13:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紫色底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過年要大紅大紫"},{"pid":"dd03ce419671308d871fb383e91ba92b3a29daab","tid":99493,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"自殺都唔好搞到人啦"},{"pid":"c90e3d4a18edcd0428c072b4c41a2e399d9b1c18","tid":99493,"uid":77077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:17:33.000Z","msg":"老虎話：正！！過年！加餸！"},{"pid":"c1c0da01b173fe033c40ae71d5861f776eea18f0","tid":99493,"uid":34001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:17: